            "content": "<p>The product helps balance female hormones (Estrogen), which is crucial for maintaining feminine traits, smooth skin, and reproductive health. It supports ovarian health, improves physiological functions, and alleviates negative symptoms of hormonal deficiency such as irregular menstrual cycles, hot flashes, and mood swings.</p>",
